<div class="site-blocks-cover" style="background-image: url(/images/banner.jpg);" data-aos="fade">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row align-items-start align-items-md-end">
            <div class="col-md-3 text-center text-md-left pt-5 pt-md-0">
                <div class="intro-text text-center text-md-left">
                    <p>
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-sm btn-primary">Mua ngay</a>
                        [{{user.email}}]
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="site-section site-section-sm site-blocks-1">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 d-lg-flex mb-4 mb-lg-0 pl-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="">
                <div class="icon mr-4 align-self-start">
                    <span class="icon-truck"></span>
                </div>
                <div class="text">
                    <h2>Miễn phí giao hàng</h2>
                    <p>Miễn phí giao hàng cho khu vực nội thành TP.HCM.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 d-lg-flex mb-4 mb-lg-0 pl-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
                <div class="icon mr-4 align-self-start">
                    <span class="icon-refresh2"></span>
                </div>
                <div class="text">
                    <h2>Đổi trả miễn phí</h2>
                    <p>1 đổi 1 trong vòng 30 ngày nếu lỗi do nhà sản xuất.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 d-lg-flex mb-4 mb-lg-0 pl-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
                <div class="icon mr-4 align-self-start">
                    <span class="icon-help"></span>
                </div>
                <div class="text">
                    <h2>Bảo hành chính hãng</h2>
                    <p>Bảo hành 12 tháng tại các trung tâm chính hãng được ủy quyền.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="site-section site-blocks-2">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            {{#each topBrand}}
                <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-6 col-lg-4 mb-4 mb-lg-0" data-aos="fade" data-aos-delay={{this.delay}}>
                    <a class="block-2-item" href="#">
                        <figure class="image">
                            <img src={{this.image}} alt="" class="img-fluid">
                        </figure>
                        <div class="text">
                            <h3>{{this.name}}</h3>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </div>
            {{/each}}
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="site-section block-3 site-blocks-2 bg-light">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-7 site-section-heading text-center pt-4">
                <h2>Bán chạy nhất</h2>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <div class="nonloop-block-3 owl-carousel">
                    {{#each hotItems}}
                        <div class="item">
                            <a href="/product{{this.uri}}">
                                <div class="block-4 text-center">
                                    <figure class="block-4-image">
                                        <img src={{this.image}} alt="Image placeholder" class="img-fluid">
                                    </figure>
                                    <div class="block-4-text p-4">
                                        <h3>{{this.name}}</h3>
                                        <p class="text-primary font-weight-bold">{{this.price}} đ</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    {{/each}}
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>